Data Structure
--------------
  Trials: 20
  Trials per class: left_hand=10, right_hand=10
  Blocks per session: 6
  Trials context: 20 trials per run (10 left, 10 right). Session 1: 4 offline runs (80 trials). Session 2: 4 online bar runs (80 trials). Sessions 3-6: 3 online bar runs each (60 trials). Total bar-feedback trials per subject: 400.

Preprocessing
-------------
  Data state: raw
  Preprocessing applied: False
  Notes: Raw EEG signals recorded in GDF format. For analysis, signals were bandpass filtered at 8-30 Hz using a second-order Butterworth filter.

